{"tid":1828852,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"（第6年）2020員工折扣交換群組 Wts","createTime":"2020-01-18T08:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:54:19.000Z","uid":75218,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4c98226b01457672e84e94757fe5ca9024362728","tid":1828852,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"交代番背景： <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />這是一個平台給各位sales界既朋友互相交換折扣，由2014年初辦群組至今已經<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6年</span></span></strong>. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每年出post , 個目的都係為左擴大群組，令大家都會分享到更多種類折扣.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現在我地大概有700人.好希望有一日做到全香港買野都會員工價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以依家又招人啦，以下為入谷要求；<br />\n<br />\n1. 必須是在職員工 ，並於表格清楚列明可提供折扣/公司<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係藍絲左膠既我勸你唔好申請</span></strong></span>。你比假資料我我唔會俾你入（每一個申請我都會check)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 光復香港之餘，死黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0/edit#response=ACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0%2Fedit%23response%3DACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=51d7a3c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0/edit#response=ACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>記得打清楚 電話，公司提供折扣</strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1f0e91285f44107f0db82c08122f1735f1ef43ac","tid":182885